title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 20 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jul 20 2022
description:
Instagram influencer, who just happens to be member of congress, AOC, and Ilhan Omar pretend to be handcuffed after arrest at abortion protest outside of Supreme Court. This used to be called insider trading: Nancy Pelosi's husband bought 20,000 shares in a semiconductor company right before an expected Senate vote for that same company. SNL Legend Dana Carvey shows off his excellent Biden impression. According to European Med Agency, “frequent booster shots could adversely affect the immune response.” The German government just admitted that 1 in 5,000 covid shots cause "serious side effects." Bill de Blasio surprised to learn New Yorkers don't want him after he ran city into the ground.
